3.title: Welcome/Info Screen
3.content:
Phoneme Perception Test Instructions

Welcome to the phoneme perception test! Please read the following instructions carefully before starting the test.

Instructions:

Ensure you are in a quiet environment and you use headphones, for better sound quality.

In each trial, you will be presented with two sounds.

The sounds will play automatically and you will have to decide if they are the same or different.

You will only hear each sound once.

Repeat this process for each set of sounds until the test is complete.
